column5: Just looking for a little clarification here, I thought that Algonquin was closed to all fishing as of the end of september, but looking at the regs today it says dec 1- dec 31, does that mean you can still fish for bass?
Yes, you can fish for Bass up until the end of November in Algonquin.
Cool! And I guess pike too?
Pike, Walleye...anything that's open until the end of Nov.
Guess there's one more trip there left to do!
Hey Chris, I know you already got your answer but here's some more info Fishing Algonquin Sept/Oct
